---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="FAQ | Auto Video">
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <section class="grid">
    <article class="card"><h3>Do I need an account?</h3><p>No. You can use the mock generator and demos instantly.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Is this real rendering?</h3><p>The create page currently mocks rendering to demonstrate the final workflow.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Can I use it for ads?</h3><p>Yes, demo formats include social ads, explainers, and storytelling reels.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Where can I get support?</h3><p>Use the contact page to send us your requirements and timelines.</p></article>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
